      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that there are two sides, but you didnt really answer my question about which perspective is more valid. can you look at the actual outcomes? like, if we look at the data, isn't it pretty clear that rights-based approaches provide better coverage? i feel like the \"inefficiency\" argument is just a way to protect private profits rather than a real policy concern.",
